text: @UPS Not sure how you weren’t able to deliver my package on Friday, but now I have to wait for you to take my package to a UPS Access Point. Why couldn’t you do that the same day you tried to deliver my package?

@powlovemx I understand your concerns and most of the time with the volume that a driver carries they are unable to deliver to the access point the same day. Normally the delivery takes place on the next business day.^QJ

@UPSHelp I got out of work early to pick up my package at your access point and was told my the owner that they had to close early and couldn’t help me. I’m not sure why you have official store hours if they are not followed. I should have received my package Friday.
